### Services (Business Logic)

#### [NEW] `CommissionService.php`
```php
// Dipanggil saat admin verifikasi payment (order lunas)
distributeCommission(Order $order): OrderCommission
// Split otomatis, credit wallet platform & vendor
```

#### [NEW] `WalletService.php`
```php
credit(User $user, amount, category, reference, description)
debit(User $user, amount, category, reference, description)
freeze(User $user, amount)    // Deposit vendor
unfreeze(User $user, amount)  // Refund deposit
```

